      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so i was cutting veggies and the knife slipped... i got a pretty deep cut on my forearm. it’s still oozing a bit but it’s not like spraying blood or anything. i have some organic honey in the kitchen, can i just put that on it and bandage it up? i really dont want to sit in an ER for hours if i dont have to",
